b1cc1678-ca94-408e-9e4b-7af169a912e2.title: Mysterious Voice 1
b1cc1678-ca94-408e-9e4b-7af169a912e2.text: Who are you and what do you want?

options.text: Roald sent me to check on Drezel.
Hi, I just moved in next door.
I hear this place is of historic interest.
The council sent me to check your pipes.

961a624f-202e-4729-982b-e71e78c0100b.title: <player>
961a624f-202e-4729-982b-e71e78c0100b.text: Hi, I just moved in next door.

6b40e1ce-1a8f-48d8-8963-bb1c32ebacbc.title: <player>
6b40e1ce-1a8f-48d8-8963-bb1c32ebacbc.text: Can I borrow a cup of coffee?

f131a84d-999f-408f-a913-6e4471fccea3.title: Mysterious Voice 1
f131a84d-999f-408f-a913-6e4471fccea3.text: What next door? What's coffee? Who ARE you?

options.text: Roald sent me to check on Drezel.
I hear this place is of historic interest.
The council sent me to check your pipes.

c75dcd15-a50e-4351-9a2c-f27862e6958f.title: <player>
c75dcd15-a50e-4351-9a2c-f27862e6958f.text: The council sent me to check your pipes.

782d17b2-bb4b-4daf-98c0-ad8c228446db.title: Mysterious Voice 1
782d17b2-bb4b-4daf-98c0-ad8c228446db.text: Psst... Are there any pipes in here, you reckon?

eed62723-50dc-4fbd-ba93-4953c0bc6267.title: Mysterious Voice 2
eed62723-50dc-4fbd-ba93-4953c0bc6267.text: I dunno... I don't think so...

eaf24861-a837-4980-8851-acdc8e85508c.title: Mysterious Voice 1
eaf24861-a837-4980-8851-acdc8e85508c.text: We don't have any thanks! Bye!

f7012dae-3ae7-4429-a2fa-fc032ba47c88.title: <player>
f7012dae-3ae7-4429-a2fa-fc032ba47c88.text: I hear this place is of historic interest.

d12c4cea-eacd-454f-98ff-4a42c9b079a8.title: <player>
d12c4cea-eacd-454f-98ff-4a42c9b079a8.text:
Can I come in and have a wander around? Possibly
look at some antiques or buy something from your gift
shop?

0fe4fa1f-cabb-4101-849b-e377b8eda58c.title: Mysterious Voice 1
0fe4fa1f-cabb-4101-849b-e377b8eda58c.text: Pssst... Hey... Is this place of historic interest?

a81d9685-94c1-4257-8d96-9867dc4bd9c5.title: Mysterious Voice 2
a81d9685-94c1-4257-8d96-9867dc4bd9c5.text: I dunno. I guess it might be. Does it matter?

60053bb4-9733-427b-bc2f-4a86609ffcbb.title: Mysterious Voice 1
60053bb4-9733-427b-bc2f-4a86609ffcbb.text: Clear off! You can't come in!

options.text: Roald sent me to check on Drezel.
Hi, I just moved in next door.
The council sent me to check your pipes.

2fbedddf-3dfc-45b2-93dd-a7ac1f694b23.title: <player>
2fbedddf-3dfc-45b2-93dd-a7ac1f694b23.text: Roald sent me to check on Drezel.

80dc90a5-29e9-49ca-a113-50a4dc3dcf38.title: Mysterious Voice 1
80dc90a5-29e9-49ca-a113-50a4dc3dcf38.text: Psst... Hey... Who's Roald? Who's Drezel?

227af90a-cbda-40c6-a68e-80b2a56a4d7c.title: Mysterious Voice 2
227af90a-cbda-40c6-a68e-80b2a56a4d7c.text:
Uh... Isn't Drezel that dude upstairs? Oh, wait, Roald's
the king of Misthalin right?

248dd257-db3c-498a-9273-987a4f4f4b1f.title: Mysterious Voice 1
248dd257-db3c-498a-9273-987a4f4f4b1f.text: Hey, you deal with this okay.

15362d12-2172-458d-9f46-9d1e16a7f98f.title: Mysterious Voice 1
15362d12-2172-458d-9f46-9d1e16a7f98f.text: He's just coming! Wait a second!

3978b4ff-aecb-4a1c-acb5-c58140b721ab.title: <player>
3978b4ff-aecb-4a1c-acb5-c58140b721ab.text:
Well, as I say, the king sent me to make sure
everything's okay with you.

46032c44-e6e1-4f1e-bc37-18fb0f1acdde.title: Mysterious Voice 2
46032c44-e6e1-4f1e-bc37-18fb0f1acdde.text: I mean Drezel. How can I help?

d4bf3c1e-2ebd-4e5a-98f3-d4973946b3c0.title: Mysterious Voice 2
d4bf3c1e-2ebd-4e5a-98f3-d4973946b3c0.text:
And, uh, what would you do if everything wasn't okay
with me?

d4d52e26-98fd-46a9-86fe-790abd72846b.title: <player>
d4d52e26-98fd-46a9-86fe-790abd72846b.text: I'm not sure. Ask you what help you need I suppose.

be929771-d9f2-489e-a963-bf3bda37cdb3.title: Mysterious Voice 2
be929771-d9f2-489e-a963-bf3bda37cdb3.text: Ah, good, well, I don't think...

022d849e-f988-4d8a-a805-13299e87addf.title: Mysterious Voice 2
022d849e-f988-4d8a-a805-13299e87addf.text: Will you do me a favour, adventurer?

options.text: Nope. Something about all this is very suspicious...

db7ccdfb-8492-4e26-85f7-4bc95f070947.title: <player>
db7ccdfb-8492-4e26-85f7-4bc95f070947.text: Nope. Something about all this is very suspicious...

e9824cb4-bce2-45cb-95d5-684d2475936c.title: Mysterious Voice 2
e9824cb4-bce2-45cb-95d5-684d2475936c.text:
Get lost then! I have important things to do, as sure as
my name is Dibzil.

23e0ed1a-da55-4b90-844f-968ce672e300.title: Mysterious Voice 2
23e0ed1a-da55-4b90-844f-968ce672e300.text:
HAHAHAHA! Really? Thanks buddy! You see that
mausoleum out there? There's a horrible big dog
underneath it that I'd like you to kill for me! It's been
really bugging me! Barking all the time and stuff!

3f1bec2a-b3a1-4b00-a149-4ac4e1e4fe1f.title: Mysterious Voice 2
3f1bec2a-b3a1-4b00-a149-4ac4e1e4fe1f.text: Please kill it for me buddy!

3290a9b1-692a-4e76-b6ad-97c143ee66ce.title: <player>
3290a9b1-692a-4e76-b6ad-97c143ee66ce.text: Okey-dokey, one dead dog coming up.

7b7f6897-a9e2-4bdd-8390-51bb8b9d20e4.title: <player>
7b7f6897-a9e2-4bdd-8390-51bb8b9d20e4.text: What am I supposed to be doing again?

ee3bd18e-478c-40c2-9f6e-fc33f36f400d.title: Mysterious Voice 1
ee3bd18e-478c-40c2-9f6e-fc33f36f400d.text:
Ah! I want you to go kill the horrible dog in the
mausoleum for me! You can use the entrance out
there.

7fc2a750-99e2-447f-9661-c860cc4af604.title: Mysterious Voice 2
7fc2a750-99e2-447f-9661-c860cc4af604.text: You'll do this for good old Delzig, won't ya buddy?

ed33a4f3-afd4-4677-9a3e-58aa7aaab1aa.title: Mysterious Voice 1
ed33a4f3-afd4-4677-9a3e-58aa7aaab1aa.text: *cough* for good old Drezel, right buddy?

479359fe-1420-465a-b3d3-679c98a83f8c.title: Mysterious Voice 1
479359fe-1420-465a-b3d3-679c98a83f8c.text: You again? What do you want now?

239b5267-8ef4-468b-9f2e-bb3ef77b1611.title: <player>
239b5267-8ef4-468b-9f2e-bb3ef77b1611.text: I killed that dog for you.

0a8c3bcc-9236-46ea-89fd-8bd48a28a11d.title: Mysterious Voice 1
0a8c3bcc-9236-46ea-89fd-8bd48a28a11d.text: Nothing buddy! We're just so grateful!

856ad381-fa77-4c57-9a09-18c726ed517e.title: Mysterious Voice 2
856ad381-fa77-4c57-9a09-18c726ed517e.text:
Yeah, maybe you should go tell the king what a great
job you did buddy!
